    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new (horror style, not violent) game in Pixel Art. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SURVIVE THE CHASING</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Unfinished 2, chases are intensified. There could be chases at any time. So be prepared for every pursuit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THE MONSTERS ARE COME BACK </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The monsters from Unfinished make a return in Unfinished 2. However, they will assist you for a while, but then they will turn against you again. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THE SERIAL KILLER </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new antagonist emerges in Unfinished 2. Mike, the serial killer, who seeks revenge on his wife. But he must realize that he should have handled his problem differently. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NEW LORE </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new and deeper backstory that explains why Mike became a serial killer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MORE INTELLIGENT ENEMIES </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The enemies are now much more intelligent.</p>",
